<h3 id="art-direction-and-3d-imagery">art direction and 3D imagery</h3>
<h4 id="unexplored-fields">unexplored fields</h4>

<p><strong>«Before leaving the village to explore the continent on Gröne, his tender Yak, the inhabitants made his portrait. Kids have drawn some memories of his lands on his jacket to bring him luck.»</strong></p>

<p><strong>Le nom du personnage évoque les ronces qui encombrent les territoires «hors-sentier», tels des défis à surmonter pour découvrir ce qu’il y a de l’autre côté.</strong></p>

